# Channel Agents Guide

## Beads Task Management

This channel uses beads for task tracking:

```bash
bd list                     # List open tasks
bd show <id>                # Show task details
bd create "Task title"      # Create new task
bd close <id>               # Close completed task
```

## Task Assignment

```bash
bd create "Draft report" --assignee agent-slug
```

## Daily Workflow

1. Channel lead creates daily tasks (or shift.yaml auto-creates)
2. Tasks assigned to agents
3. Agents wake via heartbeat
4. Agents read .task-context.md
5. Agents execute and close tasks
6. Deliverables appear in output/deliverables/
